---
import { SITE } from '~/lib/site';
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="mt-16 border-t border-zinc-200 bg-zinc-50 dark:border-zinc-800 dark:bg-zinc-900/50">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-[88rem] px-4 py-10 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">{SITE.title}.org</p>
        <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">{SITE.description}</p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">Medical disclaimer</p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          This is community-compiled information, not medical advice. Nothing here is a substitute for
          a conversation with a qualified clinician familiar with your situation. If you are in
          immediate crisis, call or text 988 (US) or your local emergency number.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">
        <p class="font-semibold text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-100">Contribute</p>
        <p class="mt-2">
          This site is community-maintained. Open an issue or pull request on
          <a href={SITE.repo} class="text-accent-700 underline decoration-accent-300 underline-offset-2 hover:decoration-accent-600 dark:text-accent-300 dark:decoration-accent-700">GitHub</a>
          to suggest a correction or addition.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col items-start justify-between gap-3 border-t border-zinc-200 pt-6 text-xs text-zinc-500 sm:flex-row sm:items-center dark:border-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-500">
      <p>© {year} {SITE.title}.org · No accounts, no tracking, no monetization.</p>
      <nav aria-label="Site footer" class="flex flex-wrap gap-x-4 gap-y-1">
        <a href="/sitemap" class="hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-200">Site map</a>
        <a href="/resources/community" class="hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-200">Community</a>
        <a href={SITE.repo} class="hover:text-zinc-900 dark:hover:text-zinc-200">GitHub</a>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
